               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Nagara Māryām "The Story of Mary" (fols. 2ra-90va)
 I–1) Reading
                     for the 21st of Yakkātit (fols. 2ra-13ra)
 I–2) Reading for the 21st of
                     Maggābit (fols. 13ra-16va)
 I–3) Reading for the 21st of Miyāzyā (fols.
                     16va-19ra)
 I–4) Reading for the 21st of Gǝnbot (fols. 19ra-22vb)
 I–5)
                     Reading for the 21st of Sane (fols. 22vb-39va)
 I–6) Reading for the 21st
                     of Ḥamle (fols. 39va-46va)
 I–7) Reading for the 21st of Naḥāse (fols.
                     46va-53ra)
 I–8) Reading for the 21st of Maskaram (fols. 53ra-55vb)
                     I–9) Reading for the 21st of Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 55vb-60ra)
 I–10) Reading for
                     the 21st of Ḫǝdār (fols. 60ra-70ra)
 I–11) Reading for the 21st of Tāḫśāś
                     (fols. 70ra-75ra)
 I–12) Reading for the 21st of Ṭǝrr (fols.
                     75ra-90va)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
